sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Estudiante
    participant FE as Frontend React
    participant API as AiController
    participant SVC as PredictiveAnalysisService
    participant GEM as GeminiPredictiveAiClient
    participant GAI as Gemini 1.5 Flash

    U->>FE: Click en "Generar ejercicios personalizados"
    FE->>API: POST /api/ai/predictive-analysis
    API->>SVC: analyze(request)
    SVC->>GEM: predict(metricas)
    GEM->>GAI: generateContent(prompt + response_mime_type JSON)
    GAI-->>GEM: JSON estructurado
    GEM-->>SVC: PredictiveAnalysisResponse
    SVC-->>API: analytics + prediction + recommendations + challenge
    API-->>FE: JSON predictivo
    FE-->>U: Actualiza panel IA y reto central

    alt Gemini falla o API key no disponible
        GEM-->>SVC: fallback estructurado
        SVC-->>API: respuesta compatible
        API-->>FE: JSON de respaldo
    end
